name: internproj
description: Data Format Assumption: It is assumed that the input CSV file has columns named 'Time', 'Time Out', 'Timecard Hours (as Time)', and 'Employee Name'. The 'Time' and 'Time Out' columns are assumed to be in a datetime format. The 'Timecard Hours (as Time)' column is assumed to be in the format '%H:%M', representing hours and minutes.
